            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

            <p>Welcome to <strong>Media Stream</strong>! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains
                  how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our video conferencing, messaging, and
                  collaboration application (the <strong>"App"</strong>).</p>

            <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p>Since Media Stream does not require account creation, we collect minimal data, including:</p>
            <ul>
                  <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Technical identifiers such as device type, operating system,
                        and IP address (for service optimization).</li>
                  <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Aggregated statistics to improve App performance.</li>
                  <li><strong>Media Data:</strong> Temporary processing of video, audio, and screen sharing during
                        active sessions. <em>We do not store this data after sessions end.</em></li>
            </ul>

            <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul>
                  <li>Provide and maintain the App’s functionality.</li>
                  <li>Monitor security and prevent abuse.</li>
                  <li>Analyze performance trends (using anonymized data).</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>3. Data Sharing and Security</h2>
            <ul>
                  <li>We <strong>do not sell</strong> or share your data with third parties for marketing purposes.</li>
                  <li>Data is secured via <strong>TLS/SSL encryption</strong> and industry-standard protections.</li>
                  <li>Session data (e.g., video streams) is <strong>automatically deleted</strong> post-call.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>4. Hosting and Infrastructure</h2>
            <ul>
                  <li>Backend services are hosted on <strong>AWS EC2</strong> with strict access controls.</li>
                  <li>Real-time communication uses <strong>Mediasoup</strong>, a WebRTC framework designed for privacy.
                  </li>
                  <li>Third-party services (e.g., AWS) comply with GDPR and similar regulations.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
            <ul>
                  <li>Media Stream does <strong>not</strong> use persistent tracking cookies.</li>
                  <li>Session cookies (if used) are temporary and essential for functionality.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
            <ul>
                  <li>No accounts = no personal data profiles. To "delete" data, simply stop using the App.</li>
                  <li>For requests, contact us at the email below.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
            <p>The App is <strong>not intended for users under 13</strong>. We do not knowingly collect their data.</p>

